covering is problems associated

00:00:41.490 --> 00:00:43.920
with first-order processes.

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:49.660
So this is just a small
introduction to this idea.

00:00:49.660 --> 00:00:52.770
So radioactive decay has
a lot of applications.

00:00:52.770 --> 00:00:56.910
There are medical applications,
including imaging organs

00:00:56.910 --> 00:00:59.000
and bones, including the heart.

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:02.160
And so there is a compound
that you already saw

00:01:02.160 --> 00:01:03.740
called Cardiolite.

