it's there so you

00:03:51.860 --> 00:03:54.800
don't have to guard it so
they can't find it and use it.

00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:57.200
But then what if
someone stumbles upon it

00:03:57.200 --> 00:03:59.920
and releases all of
this radioactivity?

00:03:59.920 --> 00:04:01.280
So that would be bad.

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:03.280
So do you put warning
signs for people

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:06.830
who will be around 100,000 years
from now, saying, hey, don't

00:04:06.830 --> 00:04:07.780
go in here.

00:04:07.780 --> 00:04:09.150
It looks like a pretty tunnel.

00:04:09.150 --> 00:04:13.470
But, hey, the half-life
of the thing stored here

00:04:13.470 --> 00:04:14.490
are 100,000 years.

00:04:14.490 --> 00:04:16.630
So this is pretty
radioactive still.

00:04:16.630 --> 00:04:17.740
Don't go inside.

00:04:17.740 --> 00:04:20.959
And if you write this sign,
what language do you put it in?

00:04:20.959 --> 00:04:25.630
So the documentary pointed
out that Neanderthals

00:04:25.630 --> 00:04:28.500
existed like 40,000 years ago.

00:04:28.500 --> 00:04:32.790
So 100,000 years from now,
what's going to be going on?

00:04:32.790 --> 00:04:36.070
How do you write a sign to
people that long in the future?

00:04:36.070 --> 00:04:39.130
