are sort of interesting ideas

00:04:39.130 --> 00:04:42.740
and brings up the point that
as scientists and engineers,

00:04:42.740 --> 00:04:44.720
we need to think not
only about the science

00:04:44.720 --> 00:04:46.250
and engineering of
what we're doing,

00:04:46.250 --> 00:04:51.660
but the ramifications to
society and the sociology

00:04:51.660 --> 00:04:54.990
as well as politics involved
in some of this science.

00:04:54.990 --> 00:04:57.970
So this is an interesting
area for that intersection

00:04:57.970 --> 00:05:00.950
of the social sciences
and the natural sciences

00:05:00.950 --> 00:05:02.980
and engineering.

