00:12:35.080 --> 00:12:36.580
it doesn't matter,
as long as you're

00:12:36.580 --> 00:12:39.010
using the first-order equation.

00:12:39.010 --> 00:12:41.680
Whether it's
concentration or activity,

00:12:41.680 --> 00:12:44.820
