00:21:16.870 --> 00:21:22.850
To bismuth and polonium,
I hoped and I beckoned.

00:21:22.850 --> 00:21:26.520
My half-life was 1
6 4 microseconds.

00:21:26.520 --> 00:21:28.600
And then finally,
