you had nearly expired.

00:21:42.940 --> 00:21:45.610
You were more demanding
than any I'd dated.

00:21:45.610 --> 00:21:49.790
And much of my energy
had been liberated.

00:21:49.790 --> 00:21:52.700
But you still weren't
happy, but you had a fix.

00:21:52.700 --> 00:21:56.020
I really like the number 206.

00:21:56.020 --> 00:21:57.960
So I waited for
years until the day

00:21:57.960 --> 00:22:03.800
which began with another
beta decay and then one more.

00:22:03.800 --> 00:22:06.950
And finally, in
