00:22:06.950 --> 00:22:09.970
to lead 206, my friend.

00:22:09.970 --> 00:22:11.200
To change any further.

00:22:11.200 --> 00:22:15.750
I wouldn't be able-- not longer
active, but happily stable.

00:22:15.750 --> 00:22:17.380
It took me a
million years to do,

00:22:17.380 --> 00:22:21.360
but look how I've changed,
and all just for you.

00:22:21.360 --> 00:22:23.240
Wait, what did you say?

00:22:23.240 --> 00:22:26.120
I've gotten so old
